# CQRS
- Many people have been getting confused over what CQRS is. They look at CQRS as being an architecture; it is not. CQRS is a very 
  simple pattern that enables many opportunities for architecture that may otherwise not exist. 
  https://web.archive.org/web/20110108231518/http://codebetter.com/gregyoung/2010/02/16/cqrs-task-based-uis-event-sourcing-agh/
